summary: This is an email exchange from January 13, 2020, regarding scheduling a presentation by defense counsel for an unspecified case. The sender apologizes for being out sick and unable to access calendars, promising to provide availability for a meeting on January 24, 2020.

events.title: Scheduled presentation by defense counsel
events.description: A presentation by defense counsel is being scheduled, with a request to block 90 minutes (or 60 minutes) for it.

keyFacts: Email exchange dated January 13, 2020, regarding scheduling a legal presentation.
The presentation by defense counsel was planned for January 24, 2020.
The sender was out sick and unable to access calendars at the time of writing.
